title: VEM Project (Live In Movement)
description: Application that provides information about free sports groups available in a city to increase public access and engagement in physical activity.

title: Green-Rocket
description: Project focused on developing solutions for a company dedicated to sustainable, efficient cultivation of medical cannabis (B2B), combining technology, environmental responsibility and innovation.

title: Around Us
description: Full stack web app where users can create an account, log in, edit profile, add image cards, like and delete cards. Built with focus on auth, front/back integration and good practices.

title: News Explorer
description: Web app that lets users search and save news articles from multiple sources using NewsAPI. Users can create accounts, search, view details and save favorites.
